  <a name="overview"> </a>
  <h3>About HL7 v2+</h3>
  <p>
    V2+ is an initiative to modernize the widespread, dependable V2 standard. It gives implementers worldwide a new and modern way to access and use the specifications. The initiative makes it easier for HL7 to develop and maintain the V2 standard as the workhorse specification of worldwide healthcare data exchange.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Enhanced navigation allowing users to move more easily through content from technical or workflow perspectives</li>
    <li>Common look and feel with other HL7 published standards</li>
    <li>More consistent content accessible from different locations in the standard</li>
    <li>New ways to represent cardinality and usage of elements</li>
    <li>Better integration with UTG terminology and conformance methodology</li>
  </ul>

